# Todo App Tech Stack

This project is a minimal todo app with:

- **Frontend:** `frontend/` — React 18, Vite 5, TypeScript, Vitest
- **Backend:** `backend/` — Java 17, Spring Boot 3.2, Maven, JPA
- **Database:** H2 (configured via `spring.datasource.url`)

## Key Paths

- `frontend/src/components/TodoList.tsx` — main UI component
- `frontend/src/components/TodoItem.tsx` — todo item with toggle/delete
- `frontend/src/api/todos.ts` — API client (getTodos, createTodo, updateTodo, deleteTodo)
- `frontend/src/types/todo.ts` — Todo type definition
- `backend/src/main/java/com/todo/` — entity, repository, service, controller
- `backend/src/main/resources/application.properties` — H2 and Spring config

## Verification

- `cd frontend && npm run test` — frontend tests
- `cd backend && ./mvnw test` — backend tests (includes H2 config, API acceptance)
